<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>How We've Helped Thousands of Clients</title>
    <style>
      body,
      table,
      td,
      p,
      a {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .hero-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2744 0%, #2c4a7c 100%);
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-banner h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .hero-banner p {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 36px 40px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a2744;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background-color: #f0f5fb;
        border-left: 4px solid #2c4a7c;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .highlight-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .highlight-box strong {
        color: #1a2744;
      }
      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #2c4a7c;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf1;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .step-item {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #444;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-footer p {
        color: #8fa3bf;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer-phone {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 12px !important;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
        .email-body,
        .email-header,
        .hero-banner,
        .email-footer {
          padding-left: 24px !important;
          padding-right: 24px !important;
        }
        .hero-banner h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <table
        class="email-container"
        role="presentation"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        width="100%"
      >
        <tr><td class="email-header"><img
              src="cid:emailLogo"
              alt="Wynn Tax Solutions"
            /></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="hero-banner">
            <h1>Years of Results. Thousands of Clients.<br />A Track Record You
              Can Trust.</h1>
            <p>See how our experience works for you</p>
          </td></tr>
        <tr><td class="email-body">
            <p class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>When it comes to resolving tax issues, experience matters. At
              Wynn Tax Solutions, we've spent years building the kind of deep,
              hands-on expertise that only comes from working with thousands of
              clients across every type of tax situation imaginable.</p>
            <table
              width="100%"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              style="margin: 24px 0;"
            >
              <tr>
                <td width="33%" align="center" style="padding: 16px 8px;">
                  <div
                    style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #2c4a7c; line-height: 1.2;"
                  >10+</div>
                  <div
                    style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"
                  >Years of Experience</div>
                </td>
                <td width="33%" align="center" style="padding: 16px 8px;">
                  <div
                    style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #2c4a7c; line-height: 1.2;"
                  >50</div>
                  <div
                    style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"
                  >States Covered</div>
                </td>
                <td width="33%" align="center" style="padding: 16px 8px;">
                  <div
                    style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #2c4a7c; line-height: 1.2;"
                  >1000s</div>
                  <div
                    style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"
                  >Clients Helped</div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            <p>From individuals facing their first IRS notice to business owners
              managing complex payroll issues, our team has guided clients
              through the full spectrum of federal and state tax challenges.
              That breadth of experience means we've likely seen a situation
              very similar to yours &mdash; and we know what works.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
              <p><strong>The kinds of clients we work with every day:</strong></p>
              <p>&#10003; Individuals who've received IRS or state collection
                notices</p>
              <p>&#10003; Self-employed professionals and freelancers with tax
                obligations</p>
              <p>&#10003; Small business owners navigating payroll and quarterly
                filings</p>
              <p>&#10003; Families going through major life changes &mdash;
                divorce, inheritance, job loss</p>
              <p>&#10003; Anyone who's fallen behind on filing and needs to get
                back on track</p>
            </div>
            <p>What sets us apart isn't just what we know &mdash; it's how we
              apply it. Every plan we build is specific to
              <em>your</em>
              numbers, your timeline, and your goals. We don't believe in
              one-size-fits-all approaches, and our results reflect that.</p>
            <hr class="divider" />
            <p
              style="font-weight:600; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:16px;"
            >What our clients value most</p>
            <div class="step-item">&#127919;
              <strong>Real-world solutions</strong>
              &mdash; Not theoretical advice. Strategies that are built for your
              actual financial picture.</div>
            <div class="step-item">&#129309;
              <strong>A team that advocates for you</strong>
              &mdash; We communicate directly with the IRS and state agencies on
              your behalf.</div>
            <div class="step-item">&#128337;
              <strong>Respect for your time</strong>
              &mdash; Clear communication, honest timelines, and no unnecessary
              delays.</div>
            <p>Let us put that experience to work for you. A conversation is the
              best place to start.</p>
            <div class="cta-wrapper"><a
                href="{{scheduleUrl}}"
                class="cta-button"
              >Schedule a Free Consultation</a></div>
            <p style="text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#666;">Or call us
              toll-free:
              <strong style="color:#1a2744;">{{phone}}</strong></p>
            <hr class="divider" />
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:#888; line-height:1.6;">You're
              receiving this email because you recently expressed interest in
              Wynn Tax Solutions. If you'd prefer not to receive follow-ups,
              simply reply and let us know.</p>
          </td></tr>
        <tr><td class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-phone">&#128222; {{phone}}</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#fff;">Wynn Tax Solutions</strong></p>
            <p>Tax Resolution &amp; Relief Services</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><a
                href="https://www.wynntaxsolutions.com"
              >wynntaxsolutions.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top:14px; font-size:11px; color:#6b829e;">&copy;
              {{year}}
              Wynn Tax Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
          </td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>